Dialogue: 0,0:00:00.05,0:00:03.69,Default,,0,0,0,,妻妹的嫩鲍无缝勾引术太犯规\N我完全没抵抗就中招了！\NFNS-122 明里紬 领衔主演
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.86,0:00:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我回来了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.06,0:00:06.99,Default,,0,0,0,,欢迎回家
Dialogue: 0,0:00:06.99,0:00:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,今天这么早啊
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.27,0:00:09.20,Default,,0,0,0,,上班真是累散架了...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.20,0:00:11.55,Default,,0,0,0,,手头的大项目总算是告一段落了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.55,0:00:13.13,Default,,0,0,0,,辛苦啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.13,0:00:16.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这个周末我想在家里彻底瘫着
Dialogue: 0,0:00:19.20,0:00:20.06,Default,,0,0,0,,让您久等了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.06,0:00:20.43,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.43,0:00:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.42,0:00:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,哦？那是...紬酱？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.57,0:00:31.44,Default,,0,0,0,,姐夫，好久不见
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.08,0:00:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,她说和同居的男朋友吵了一架，离家出走了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.84,0:00:37.05,Default,,0,0,0,,吵架？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.05,0:00:40.42,Default,,0,0,0,,所以这周末想在我们家借住几天
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.92,0:00:41.45,Default,,0,0,0,,可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.45,0:00:42.74,Default,,0,0,0,,姐夫...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.06,0:00:46.34,Default,,0,0,0,,啊...我这边是完全没问题
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.18,0:00:48.52,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧，我就说吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.52,0:00:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,我就知道姐夫最温柔了，一定会答应的
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.52,0:00:55.44,Default,,0,0,0,,真是的，紬总是这么任性
Dialogue: 0,0:00:55.78,0:00:58.95,Default,,0,0,0,,既然住下了，家务活可得帮忙分担哦
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.95,0:01:00.50,Default,,0,0,0,,好~
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.74,0:01:11.64,Default,,0,0,0,,要守规矩一点哦
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.54,0:01:22.90,Default,,0,0,0,,姐夫，谢谢你收留我
Dialogue: 0,0:01:45.04,0:01:49.30,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉啊，紬突然跑来打扰
Dialogue: 0,0:01:49.66,0:01:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,没事，真的没关系
Dialogue: 0,0:01:51.94,0:01:55.96,Default,,0,0,0,,难得你以为周末能享受二人世界的
Dialogue: 0,0:01:58.12,0:02:00.15,Default,,0,0,0,,不用把她当客人对待
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.15,0:02:01.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那孩子啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:02.40,0:02:05.18,Default,,0,0,0,,要是她懒懒散散的，你就拿出姐夫的威严教训她
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.72,0:02:07.32,Default,,0,0,0,,知道啦
Dialogue: 0,0:02:07.32,0:02:10.24,Default,,0,0,0,,真的不用顾虑那么多
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.56,0:02:12.16,Default,,0,0,0,,那我先睡了
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.16,0:02:14.24,Default,,0,0,0,,晚安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.49,0:02:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.14,0:02:52.47,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.47,0:02:55.50,Default,,0,0,0,,刚才出门了
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.98,0:03:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,紬，吃早饭了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.16,0:03:22.28,Default,,0,0,0,,还没...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:25.19,Default,,0,0,0,,那我顺便做一份吧
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.19,0:03:26.54,Default,,0,0,0,,真的吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.54,0:03:27.80,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了！
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.34,0:03:56.49,Default,,0,0,0,,睡得真快...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.49,0:03:58.90,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟是毫无防备的小姨子啊
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.34,0:04:02.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不行不行，用那种眼光看亲戚太差劲了
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.18,0:04:41.05,Default,,0,0,0,,紬，早饭做好了哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.05,0:04:46.06,Default,,0,0,0,,完全睡死过去了啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.14,0:07:05.68,Default,,0,0,0,,姐夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.68,0:07:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,紬...不，那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:10.74,0:07:14.69,Default,,0,0,0,,看你睡着了，怕你会着凉...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.69,0:07:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,早安
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.80,0:07:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,不，我真的什么都没做...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.16,0:07:27.56,Default,,0,0,0,,姐夫...你是想...再多看看我的内裤吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.26,0:07:39.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我会替你对姐姐保密的哦
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:42.06,Default,,0,0,0,,其实，还想摸摸看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.62,0:08:18.88,Default,,0,0,0,,果然不太好吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.90,0:08:22.18,Default,,0,0,0,,可是，你刚才一直盯着那里看吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.18,0:08:23.42,Default,,0,0,0,,盯着这条肉缝...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.70,0:08:28.40,Default,,0,0,0,,真的可以吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.42,0:08:31.98,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们两个人的秘密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.26,0:08:45.28,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉...我失礼了...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.96,0:08:59.78,Default,,0,0,0,,要是被姐姐知道...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.64,0:09:13.40,Default,,0,0,0,,只是稍微摸一下的话，不会被发现的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:09:15.00,0:09:18.18,Default,,0,0,0,,因为你摸得那么色情，我都被弄醒了
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.56,0:09:26.94,Default,,0,0,0,,这个...要保密哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.20,0:09:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,这种事，怎么可能说得出口
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.28,0:09:44.82,Default,,0,0,0,,好有弹性的触感...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.56,0:09:46.96,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:16.04,0:10:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下，别那样掐着肉缝揉...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.84,0:10:21.72,Default,,0,0,0,,因为，手感太好了...很痛吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.64,0:10:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，你在弄哪里啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.98,0:10:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这里的肉太软糯Q弹了...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.84,0:11:00.36,Default,,0,0,0,,你在偷看内裤对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:00.62,0:11:04.60,Default,,0,0,0,,是让你摸，不是让你看啊
Dialogue: 0,0:11:29.10,0:11:31.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你就这么喜欢我的私处吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.74,0:11:36.39,Default,,0,0,0,,这么柔软...又这么饱满...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:36.39,0:11:39.01,Default,,0,0,0,,很少见吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.01,0:11:40.66,Default,,0,0,0,,也许吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.66,0:11:44.32,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害...隔着内裤都湿透了
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.90,0:11:49.74,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.78,0:11:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然...确实很舒服...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.38,0:12:16.66,Default,,0,0,0,,越来越湿了...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:20.36,Default,,0,0,0,,要是再这样摸下去的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.41,0:13:00.28,Default,,0,0,0,,呐，不是说只摸一下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:00.39,0:13:07.06,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉...因为你的反应看起来太舒服了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.47,0:13:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这样张开腿好害羞啊...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.73,0:13:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,已经湿得一塌糊涂了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.40,0:13:23.95,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.70,0:13:34.62,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微...这姿势太不知羞耻了...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.50,0:14:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,身体...变得好热...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.50,0:14:05.74,Default,,0,0,0,,等等，你要干嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.60,0:14:09.68,Default,,0,0,0,,会有味道的...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.48,0:14:16.04,Default,,0,0,0,,再继续就糟糕了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.09,0:14:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,不行啦...太羞耻了...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.52,0:14:23.74,Default,,0,0,0,,小声点...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.18,0:14:36.24,Default,,0,0,0,,在干什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.16,0:14:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下...别掰开那里...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.66,0:16:28.56,Default,,0,0,0,,明明说好只给看看内裤的...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.56,0:16:31.68,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉...没忍住...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.16,0:16:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,没办法，这次就算了...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.36,0:16:37.16,Default,,0,0,0,,从后面摸...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.54,0:16:41.46,Default,,0,0,0,,馒头的形状好漂亮...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.36,0:16:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,摸法好奇怪...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.22,0:17:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,发出这种声音的话...越来越湿了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.86,0:17:11.46,Default,,0,0,0,,姐夫一副很享受的表情呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.24,0:17:30.44,Default,,0,0,0,,呐，想舔吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.30,0:17:56.06,Default,,0,0,0,,我有说可以舔吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.06,0:17:59.13,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.38,0:18:08.48,Default,,0,0,0,,如果你能让我舒服的话...也可以哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:44.68,0:18:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,舔我...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.34,0:18:55.48,Default,,0,0,0,,再多舔舔...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.52,0:19:09.16,Default,,0,0,0,,呐，姐夫...稍微...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.16,0:19:11.09,Default,,0,0,0,,感觉不奇怪吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:29.02,0:19:31.51,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.51,0:19:33.57,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.57,0:19:35.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好色哦，这个水声...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.94,0:19:37.70,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:19:37.96,0:19:40.72,Default,,0,0,0,,看吧，要高潮了...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.98,0:19:52.50,Default,,0,0,0,,呐，再用力舔...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.82,0:20:04.10,Default,,0,0,0,,忍着可不行...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.32,0:20:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,要被舔得高潮了...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.07,0:20:27.47,Default,,0,0,0,,被这样盯着下面好害羞...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.10,0:20:45.08,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么了，姐夫？
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.88,0:20:59.41,Default,,0,0,0,,裤子里鼓鼓的是什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.16,0:21:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,一直忍着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.30,0:21:16.28,Default,,0,0,0,,像个发情的女孩子一样呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.08,0:22:07.54,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微...有点太舒服了...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.34,0:22:19.56,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以尽情舔个够吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:22:27.52,0:22:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,既然我的私处都被你那样玩弄了...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.72,0:22:37.72,Default,,0,0,0,,可以哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:08.06,0:23:12.55,Default,,0,0,0,,不行吗？不舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.55,0:23:15.12,Default,,0,0,0,,明明不行的？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:15.62,0:23:22.22,Default,,0,0,0,,明明那么色情地玩弄了我的肉缝...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.54,0:23:24.96,Default,,0,0,0,,姐夫的下面也给我看看吧
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.42,0:23:35.74,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么呀？
Dialogue: 0,0:23:39.54,0:23:43.00,Default,,0,0,0,,变得好精神了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.88,0:23:51.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我要仔细看看咯
Dialogue: 0,0:23:56.40,0:24:09.24,Default,,0,0,0,,果然很害羞呢？明明把我的小穴摸了个遍
Dialogue: 0,0:24:11.60,0:24:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,好大啊，姐夫
Dialogue: 0,0:24:22.98,0:24:25.40,Default,,0,0,0,,嘴里能含得下吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.12,0:24:34.46,Default,,0,0,0,,第一次含这个...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:43.60,0:25:47.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:11.22,0:26:14.22,Default,,0,0,0,,还没射呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:14.56,0:26:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好久没被这么服务了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:16.94,0:26:18.48,Default,,0,0,0,,是...是的...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:33.66,0:26:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,忍耐力真好...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:37.86,0:26:41.70,Default,,0,0,0,,再继续下去就...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:42.18,0:26:43.36,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:43.36,0:26:46.86,Default,,0,0,0,,再继续下去果然不太妙吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:50.38,0:26:52.16,Default,,0,0,0,,什么嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:54.74,0:26:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,已经忍不住想插进去了吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:26:57.74,0:27:01.14,Default,,0,0,0,,但是姐姐会不会突然回来啊？
Dialogue: 0,0:27:01.14,0:27:03.94,Default,,0,0,0,,那就糟糕了呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:06.54,0:27:10.20,Default,,0,0,0,,那就趁她回来之前...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.50,0:27:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,内裤都已经变得这么湿哒哒了...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:58.08,0:27:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,只是蹭蹭哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.76,0:28:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,只是？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:02.82,0:28:06.46,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微蹭一下肉缝应该没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.72,0:28:19.73,Default,,0,0,0,,只是蹭蹭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:28:19.73,0:28:22.92,Default,,0,0,0,,对，只是蹭蹭...
Dialogue: 0,0:28:58.60,0:29:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,但是只能蹭蹭对吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:03.34,0:29:09.46,Default,,0,0,0,,再过分就糟糕了呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:14.76,0:29:17.52,Default,,0,0,0,,但是要保持这样被肉棒顶着吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:17.52,0:29:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,姐夫...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.08,0:29:23.91,Default,,0,0,0,,不行了...可能要不行了...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:44.58,0:29:47.30,Default,,0,0,0,,要进去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:48.00,0:29:50.13,Default,,0,0,0,,是不是进来了？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:50.13,0:29:52.54,Default,,0,0,0,,已经进去了哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:53.00,0:29:54.74,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了？
Dialogue: 0,0:29:57.46,0:29:59.38,Default,,0,0,0,,骗人的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:01.64,0:30:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,自己滑进去了...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.28,0:30:06.64,Default,,0,0,0,,因为这里太多汁滑溜溜的嘛...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.30,0:30:11.73,Default,,0,0,0,,会完全进去的哦？
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.73,0:30:13.90,Default,,0,0,0,,既然都进去了...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.80,0:30:23.16,Default,,0,0,0,,真的进去了...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:23.16,0:30:24.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好大...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.82,0:30:37.08,Default,,0,0,0,,姐夫...好棒...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:38.50,0:30:41.74,Default,,0,0,0,,整根都进去了...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:41.74,0:30:44.76,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:48.42,0:30:57.92,Default,,0,0,0,,这只是偶然滑进去的，所以不算出轨吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:58.50,0:31:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然是亲戚...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:02.26,0:31:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系的吧...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:09.06,0:31:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,但是你的腰动得很厉害哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:17.28,0:31:22.58,Default,,0,0,0,,我也...好舒服...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:34.16,0:31:37.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害...肉棒...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:37.30,0:31:42.80,Default,,0,0,0,,太棒了...
Dialogue: 0,0:31:46.72,0:31:49.28,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐还在吗？不会回来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:31:54.60,0:31:56.92,Default,,0,0,0,,还要深处？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:11.80,0:32:15.00,Default,,0,0,0,,插到底了...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:16.08,0:32:18.90,Default,,0,0,0,,超级舒服...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:18.90,0:32:23.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.50,0:32:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:32:28.26,0:32:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,不用管我...用力操我...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:42.20,0:32:43.60,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕...
Dialogue: 0,0:32:43.60,0:32:46.58,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:14.34,0:33:16.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:19.24,0:33:22.32,Default,,0,0,0,,进来了...
Dialogue: 0,0:33:28.22,0:33:31.48,Default,,0,0,0,,喜欢被这样插吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.82,0:34:09.30,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:12.46,0:34:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服啊，姐夫...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.00,0:34:39.68,Default,,0,0,0,,没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:39.68,0:34:41.52,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会做过头了？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:43.40,0:34:48.42,Default,,0,0,0,,只要当做两个人的秘密就没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:51.78,0:34:54.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我也能动吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:34:57.16,0:34:59.69,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害...
Dialogue: 0,0:34:59.69,0:35:02.08,Default,,0,0,0,,结合的地方看得好清楚哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.18,0:35:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:09.62,0:35:11.50,Default,,0,0,0,,能看到插进去的地方吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:35:11.70,0:35:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,插得好深哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.70,0:35:23.14,Default,,0,0,0,,全部都进去了...
Dialogue: 0,0:35:24.02,0:35:30.40,Default,,0,0,0,,我的小穴里插着姐夫的肉棒呢...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.82,0:36:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.04,0:36:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:31.40,0:36:35.22,Default,,0,0,0,,姐夫，超级舒服哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:40.98,0:36:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害...
Dialogue: 0,0:36:42.42,0:36:44.90,Default,,0,0,0,,稍等，不行...要去了...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.48,0:37:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,超级舒服...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:10.10,0:37:12.90,Default,,0,0,0,,姐夫...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.96,0:37:28.26,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.78,0:37:59.74,Default,,0,0,0,,那样也很舒服...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:01.04,0:38:03.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.04,0:38:21.60,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.60,0:38:25.22,Default,,0,0,0,,不快点的话就要暴露了...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.22,0:38:27.18,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐快回来了吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.18,0:38:30.66,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.28,0:38:42.48,Default,,0,0,0,,这个好舒服...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.98,0:39:10.80,Default,,0,0,0,,屁股好暖和...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:23.08,0:39:27.28,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，射了好多...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:38.40,0:39:44.52,Default,,0,0,0,,全都射出来了...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.50,0:39:56.36,Default,,0,0,0,,这是我们两个人的秘密哦...
Dialogue: 0,0:40:11.20,0:40:13.69,Default,,0,0,0,,我吃饱了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:16.64,0:40:19.31,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，还特意把盘子拿过来了
Dialogue: 0,0:40:19.31,0:40:21.18,Default,,0,0,0,,我来帮忙洗吧
Dialogue: 0,0:40:21.18,0:40:23.62,Default,,0,0,0,,不用了，姐姐来洗就好
Dialogue: 0,0:40:28.16,0:40:30.98,Default,,0,0,0,,抱歉，谢啦
Dialogue: 0,0:40:36.74,0:40:38.10,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:40:45.58,0:40:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,今天吃什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:47.27,0:40:48.28,Default,,0,0,0,,晚饭吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:49.08,0:40:51.18,Default,,0,0,0,,吃什么好呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:40:51.38,0:40:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,我也吃得太饱了，脑子转不动
Dialogue: 0,0:40:55.70,0:40:58.32,Default,,0,0,0,,不过中午的咖喱真好吃啊
Dialogue: 0,0:40:58.32,0:41:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,会不会太辣了？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:00.20,0:41:02.32,Default,,0,0,0,,刚刚好哦
Dialogue: 0,0:41:04.16,0:41:07.74,Default,,0,0,0,,既然中午吃了咖喱，晚上就吃清淡点的？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:07.74,0:41:09.03,Default,,0,0,0,,确实
Dialogue: 0,0:41:09.03,0:41:10.16,Default,,0,0,0,,意大利面之类的？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.16,0:41:11.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不错呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:11.66,0:41:13.19,Default,,0,0,0,,明太子的好
Dialogue: 0,0:41:13.19,0:41:15.42,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的很喜欢明太子呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:17.12,0:41:20.12,Default,,0,0,0,,明太子和什么配呢
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.12,0:41:22.41,Default,,0,0,0,,加了大叶的意大利面？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:22.41,0:41:24.56,Default,,0,0,0,,好像很好吃
Dialogue: 0,0:41:27.82,0:41:29.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好期待
Dialogue: 0,0:41:35.22,0:41:37.34,Default,,0,0,0,,待会去买点炸的东西吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:37.34,0:41:39.28,Default,,0,0,0,,去站前的蛋糕店？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:39.28,0:41:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,不错耶
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.38,0:41:43.24,Default,,0,0,0,,你也很喜欢的吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:41:44.64,0:41:48.04,Default,,0,0,0,,那家的芝士蛋糕超好吃的
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.94,0:41:51.96,Default,,0,0,0,,久违地去买点咖啡吧
Dialogue: 0,0:41:52.64,0:41:54.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好啊
Dialogue: 0,0:41:54.36,0:41:56.54,Default,,0,0,0,,偶尔也要享受一下嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.48,0:42:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,呐，你看了我的内裤对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.68,0:42:14.66,Default,,0,0,0,,啊...看了...
Dialogue: 0,0:42:16.00,0:42:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐在呢，不可以哦
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.92,0:42:22.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我没看哦（慌张）
Dialogue: 0,0:42:32.36,0:42:34.64,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，勺子掉了
Dialogue: 0,0:42:35.36,0:42:37.30,Default,,0,0,0,,姐夫，帮我捡一下
Dialogue: 0,0:42:55.48,0:42:59.10,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐~
Dialogue: 0,0:43:11.38,0:43:13.08,Default,,0,0,0,,捡起来了
Dialogue: 0,0:44:37.54,0:44:41.44,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐~
Dialogue: 0,0:44:43.18,0:44:45.19,Default,,0,0,0,,能不能去买点洗洁精？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:45.19,0:44:46.40,Default,,0,0,0,,洗洁精？
Dialogue: 0,0:44:46.40,0:44:48.75,Default,,0,0,0,,我去刷浴缸
Dialogue: 0,0:44:48.75,0:44:50.10,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了
Dialogue: 0,0:45:25.72,0:45:27.13,Default,,0,0,0,,谢谢
Dialogue: 0,0:45:27.13,0:45:29.67,Default,,0,0,0,,姐夫，我来帮忙
Dialogue: 0,0:45:30.40,0:45:32.76,Default,,0,0,0,,你没事吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:32.76,0:45:35.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没关系啦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:38.74,0:45:41.42,Default,,0,0,0,,姐夫，我去刷浴缸了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:45:41.94,0:45:48.25,Default,,0,0,0,,呐，刚才你摸我下面的时候
Dialogue: 0,0:45:48.25,0:45:50.54,Default,,0,0,0,,这里变大了对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:45:55.16,0:46:02.78,Default,,0,0,0,,明明姐姐就在旁边，却对我的那里那么着迷，这可不行哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:04.94,0:46:08.20,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀，不是要洗浴缸吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:08.20,0:46:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,这边也要刷
Dialogue: 0,0:46:14.02,0:46:16.00,Default,,0,0,0,,你的腰在往后躲哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:16.00,0:46:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,但是...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:21.16,0:46:24.62,Default,,0,0,0,,哎呀，快点弄啦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:27.34,0:46:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,安静点...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:29.80,0:46:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,她还在楼上呢，这实在太...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:32.48,0:46:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,有什么关系嘛？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:35.62,0:46:37.00,Default,,0,0,0,,很糟糕吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:37.00,0:46:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样？
Dialogue: 0,0:46:39.94,0:46:43.68,Default,,0,0,0,,但是，刚才你摸了我的肉缝嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:46:43.68,0:46:45.56,Default,,0,0,0,,那是...
Dialogue: 0,0:46:49.16,0:46:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,这里，已经完全勃起了哦
Dialogue: 0,0:46:52.94,0:46:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊
Dialogue: 0,0:47:02.38,0:47:04.18,Default,,0,0,0,,就在浴室里掏出来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:47:36.40,0:47:39.20,Default,,0,0,0,,掏出来嘛
Dialogue: 0,0:48:04.30,0:48:06.16,Default,,0,0,0,,必须得弄好这附近才行...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:06.16,0:48:08.02,Default,,0,0,0,,这实在太糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:48:08.02,0:48:10.10,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:11.48,0:48:13.89,Default,,0,0,0,,明明刚才摸过我了？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:13.89,0:48:15.64,Default,,0,0,0,,那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:18.54,0:48:20.16,Default,,0,0,0,,能停下来吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:20.16,0:48:23.86,Default,,0,0,0,,不，现在有点...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:29.16,0:48:32.30,Default,,0,0,0,,因为姐姐在所以害怕吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:33.28,0:48:35.52,Default,,0,0,0,,毕竟...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:36.98,0:48:39.34,Default,,0,0,0,,得趁她不在的时候才行...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:40.58,0:48:41.72,Default,,0,0,0,,等一下
Dialogue: 0,0:48:41.72,0:48:43.90,Default,,0,0,0,,明明都变得这么硬了？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:43.90,0:48:45.66,Default,,0,0,0,,不，那个...
Dialogue: 0,0:48:49.00,0:48:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,其实很兴奋对吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:48:54.90,0:48:57.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害，这里硬邦邦的
Dialogue: 0,0:48:58.98,0:49:01.18,Default,,0,0,0,,别顶着我啊
Dialogue: 0,0:49:17.82,0:49:20.52,Default,,0,0,0,,要安静一点才行
Dialogue: 0,0:49:20.74,0:49:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐会下来的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:24.76,0:49:27.36,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然是这样，稍微...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:27.78,0:49:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕，声音...
Dialogue: 0,0:49:29.62,0:49:32.32,Default,,0,0,0,,呐，不行啦
Dialogue: 0,0:49:36.14,0:49:38.42,Default,,0,0,0,,呐，会发出水声的
Dialogue: 0,0:49:39.28,0:49:42.28,Default,,0,0,0,,只要不被姐姐发现就好了吧
Dialogue: 0,0:50:04.44,0:50:06.68,Default,,0,0,0,,糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:50:26.92,0:50:29.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:50:29.12,0:50:31.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好糟糕
Dialogue: 0,0:50:32.60,0:50:33.58,Default,,0,0,0,,声音...
Dialogue: 0,0:50:33.58,0:50:35.70,Default,,0,0,0,,哪里糟糕了？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:36.14,0:50:38.68,Default,,0,0,0,,真的，在这里不行
Dialogue: 0,0:50:38.68,0:50:40.14,Default,,0,0,0,,为什么？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:40.64,0:50:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的啦
Dialogue: 0,0:50:43.18,0:50:45.98,Default,,0,0,0,,刷浴缸本来就要花点时间的
Dialogue: 0,0:50:48.20,0:50:51.10,Default,,0,0,0,,因为都变成这样了
Dialogue: 0,0:50:51.84,0:50:54.24,Default,,0,0,0,,这样去见姐姐合适吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:50:56.08,0:50:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,保密哦
Dialogue: 0,0:50:59.52,0:51:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,必须得让它消下去
Dialogue: 0,0:51:03.14,0:51:05.38,Default,,0,0,0,,这儿好硬
Dialogue: 0,0:51:10.96,0:51:13.28,Default,,0,0,0,,这是什么啊？（硬邦邦的）
Dialogue: 0,0:51:53.44,0:51:55.36,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:17.80,0:52:19.72,Default,,0,0,0,,不安静点的话...
Dialogue: 0,0:52:19.72,0:52:21.30,Default,,0,0,0,,我知道
Dialogue: 0,0:52:36.13,0:52:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,勃起得好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:52:46.18,0:52:48.30,Default,,0,0,0,,这该怎么办呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:51.16,0:52:53.62,Default,,0,0,0,,就保持这样吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:52:59.82,0:53:02.84,Default,,0,0,0,,不让它消下去不行吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:04.52,0:53:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,要怎么做才能消下去呢？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:27.32,0:53:29.76,Default,,0,0,0,,这个硬硬的东西
Dialogue: 0,0:53:30.50,0:53:33.77,Default,,0,0,0,,要不要用我的馒头逼夹住它呢
Dialogue: 0,0:53:33.77,0:53:35.68,Default,,0,0,0,,什么意思？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:38.82,0:53:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,像这样...
Dialogue: 0,0:53:44.02,0:53:46.66,Default,,0,0,0,,夹住了
Dialogue: 0,0:53:54.01,0:53:55.81,Default,,0,0,0,,没做过这种素股吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:53:55.81,0:53:58.04,Default,,0,0,0,,是...是的
Dialogue: 0,0:54:10.80,0:54:11.84,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么样？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:11.84,0:54:13.60,Default,,0,0,0,,湿湿的...
Dialogue: 0,0:54:18.78,0:54:21.22,Default,,0,0,0,,肉缝很温暖吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:21.22,0:54:23.26,Default,,0,0,0,,很温暖
Dialogue: 0,0:54:46.54,0:54:48.54,Default,,0,0,0,,是吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:54:49.16,0:54:52.38,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐也会这样用肉缝磨你吗？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:03.54,0:55:05.13,Default,,0,0,0,,小穴...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:05.13,0:55:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,贴上来磨得好紧哦
Dialogue: 0,0:55:26.74,0:55:29.03,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:55:29.03,0:55:32.20,Default,,0,0,0,,肉缝摩擦得好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:55:33.16,0:55:35.48,Default,,0,0,0,,很温暖吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:55:38.84,0:55:41.64,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害...
Dialogue: 0,0:55:51.82,0:55:53.96,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:55:54.92,0:55:57.62,Default,,0,0,0,,害羞的地方被看见了
Dialogue: 0,0:56:20.82,0:56:23.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:56:36.44,0:56:41.32,Default,,0,0,0,,肉缝被这样摩擦着，好舒服
Dialogue: 0,0:57:03.16,0:57:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,0:57:11.26,0:57:14.96,Default,,0,0,0,,要是现在姐姐来了就糟糕了
Dialogue: 0,0:57:19.02,0:57:24.07,Default,,0,0,0,,因为姐姐可能会来
Dialogue: 0,0:57:24.07,0:57:26.28,Default,,0,0,0,,我躲到下面去
Dialogue: 0,0:57:26.28,0:57:30.08,Default,,0,0,0,,你看
Dialogue: 0,0:57:31.94,0:57:35.26,Default,,0,0,0,,这样的话就算她来了也没事吧？
Dialogue: 0,0:57:45.92,0:57:57.38,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服过头了
Dialogue: 0,0:58:56.56,0:58:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,得安静一点
Dialogue: 0,0:59:55.66,1:00:00.12,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:01.46,1:00:05.06,Default,,0,0,0,,其实今晚也很兴奋对吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:00:05.40,1:00:08.12,Default,,0,0,0,,超级兴奋
Dialogue: 0,1:00:08.86,1:00:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,在做坏事呢
Dialogue: 0,1:00:45.44,1:00:50.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好硬啊
Dialogue: 0,1:00:56.84,1:01:00.21,Default,,0,0,0,,变得这么硬邦邦的，打算怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:00.21,1:01:02.00,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办呢...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:03.42,1:01:07.20,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐要是看到这个会吓一跳吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:08.64,1:01:10.59,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:12.20,1:01:13.94,Default,,0,0,0,,想放进去...
Dialogue: 0,1:01:16.22,1:01:18.44,Default,,0,0,0,,在这里做吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:44.98,1:01:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,怎么办？
Dialogue: 0,1:01:56.28,1:01:58.84,Default,,0,0,0,,要放进这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:02:00.24,1:02:02.20,Default,,0,0,0,,不能放进去...
Dialogue: 0,1:02:05.62,1:02:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,虽然想放进去
Dialogue: 0,1:02:10.54,1:02:13.54,Default,,0,0,0,,我也湿了
Dialogue: 0,1:03:01.34,1:03:03.70,Default,,0,0,0,,进去了...
Dialogue: 0,1:04:16.06,1:04:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,全部射出来
Dialogue: 0,1:04:24.84,1:04:26.62,Default,,0,0,0,,会弄湿的
Dialogue: 0,1:05:01.93,1:05:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,好湿啊
Dialogue: 0,1:05:11.38,1:05:15.72,Default,,0,0,0,,亲我...
Dialogue: 0,1:05:43.28,1:05:45.52,Default,,0,0,0,,做那种事不行啦
Dialogue: 0,1:05:46.32,1:05:48.70,Default,,0,0,0,,做那种事不行啦
Dialogue: 0,1:06:16.86,1:06:19.78,Default,,0,0,0,,关掉水流可不行
Dialogue: 0,1:06:20.92,1:06:23.59,Default,,0,0,0,,湿了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:13.32,1:08:15.92,Default,,0,0,0,,姐姐来了
Dialogue: 0,1:08:20.42,1:08:23.12,Default,,0,0,0,,会被看到的
Dialogue: 0,1:09:15.90,1:09:18.41,Default,,0,0,0,,啊，浴缸洗洁精用完了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:18.41,1:09:19.55,Default,,0,0,0,,用完了？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:19.55,1:09:20.98,Default,,0,0,0,,真的？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:20.98,1:09:22.34,Default,,0,0,0,,咦？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:22.56,1:09:23.84,Default,,0,0,0,,之前不是买了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:23.84,1:09:25.63,Default,,0,0,0,,好像也没存货了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:25.63,1:09:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,那我去稍微买一点？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:28.44,1:09:29.80,Default,,0,0,0,,紬呢？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:29.80,1:09:30.88,Default,,0,0,0,,紬？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:30.88,1:09:32.38,Default,,0,0,0,,咦，刚才还在的啊
Dialogue: 0,1:09:32.38,1:09:33.73,Default,,0,0,0,,不在吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:33.73,1:09:35.24,Default,,0,0,0,,去哪了？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:35.58,1:09:37.24,Default,,0,0,0,,我也不太清楚
Dialogue: 0,1:09:37.46,1:09:39.17,Default,,0,0,0,,顺便买晚饭回来吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.17,1:09:39.93,Default,,0,0,0,,拜托了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:39.93,1:09:41.21,Default,,0,0,0,,晚上吃意面对吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:41.21,1:09:42.42,Default,,0,0,0,,意面就行
Dialogue: 0,1:09:42.42,1:09:43.84,Default,,0,0,0,,还要别的吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:09:44.46,1:09:46.35,Default,,0,0,0,,洗洁精也追加一下
Dialogue: 0,1:09:46.35,1:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,知道了知道了
Dialogue: 0,1:09:47.27,1:09:48.88,Default,,0,0,0,,路上小心
Dialogue: 0,1:09:57.68,1:09:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,吓死我了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:01.82,1:10:04.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好险啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:05.36,1:10:07.12,Default,,0,0,0,,没暴露吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:07.42,1:10:09.48,Default,,0,0,0,,好像没暴露
Dialogue: 0,1:10:11.24,1:10:13.10,Default,,0,0,0,,太好了
Dialogue: 0,1:10:14.02,1:10:15.90,Default,,0,0,0,,没事的吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:20.88,1:10:23.40,Default,,0,0,0,,去那边继续吧
Dialogue: 0,1:10:23.40,1:10:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,那边？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:31.90,1:10:36.44,Default,,0,0,0,,紬？
Dialogue: 0,1:10:47.08,1:10:50.20,Default,,0,0,0,,已经出门了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:10:51.26,1:10:52.65,Default,,0,0,0,,她短时间不会回来的
Dialogue: 0,1:10:52.65,1:10:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,没事
Dialogue: 0,1:10:59.24,1:11:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,不在哦
Dialogue: 0,1:11:37.70,1:11:39.55,Default,,0,0,0,,继续刚才的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:11:39.55,1:11:41.60,Default,,0,0,0,,从后面插进来
Dialogue: 0,1:12:16.68,1:12:19.24,Default,,0,0,0,,不能发出声音了
Dialogue: 0,1:12:23.00,1:12:26.70,Default,,0,0,0,,可以出声了吧？
Dialogue: 0,1:12:26.70,1:12:28.02,Default,,0,0,0,,出声吧
Dialogue: 0,1:12:29.82,1:12:32.34,Default,,0,0,0,,不能出声...
Dialogue: 0,1:12:48.92,1:12:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,紬，我好喜欢你
Dialogue: 0,1:13:31.00,1:13:33.98,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:13:42.44,1:13:46.04,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害...
Dialogue: 0,1:14:32.60,1:14:35.36,Default,,0,0,0,,能看见什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:37.44,1:23:39.21,Default,,0,0,0,,不，抱歉
Dialogue: 0,1:23:39.21,1:23:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,我没看
Dialogue: 0,1:23:41.82,1:23:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,因为昨天没做成，所以欲求不满了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:23:46.56,1:23:48.80,Default,,0,0,0,,不，不是的
Dialogue: 0,1:23:50.62,1:23:53.42,Default,,0,0,0,,今天姐姐回来很晚
Dialogue: 0,1:24:08.96,1:24:14.80,Default,,0,0,0,,呐，听说姐姐今天很晚才回来
Dialogue: 0,1:24:15.34,1:24:17.32,Default,,0,0,0,,尽情地做色色的事吧
Dialogue: 0,1:26:09.34,1:26:12.06,Default,,0,0,0,,抖得好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:26:14.54,1:26:18.84,Default,,0,0,0,,今天姐姐不在，可以尽情发出声音哦
Dialogue: 0,1:26:47.44,1:26:50.16,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:26:57.75,1:26:59.46,Default,,0,0,0,,可以舔吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:08.48,1:28:12.26,Default,,0,0,0,,身体抖成这样，有那么舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:26.80,1:28:29.00,Default,,0,0,0,,已经硬了
Dialogue: 0,1:28:31.14,1:28:34.04,Default,,0,0,0,,从什么时候开始硬的？
Dialogue: 0,1:28:42.72,1:28:44.58,Default,,0,0,0,,可以看吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:07.74,1:29:09.00,Default,,0,0,0,,什么？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:09.60,1:29:12.22,Default,,0,0,0,,又想看小穴？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:12.86,1:29:16.14,Default,,0,0,0,,姐夫真是个变态呢
Dialogue: 0,1:29:23.52,1:29:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这样
Dialogue: 0,1:29:34.12,1:29:35.90,Default,,0,0,0,,哎？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:37.38,1:29:41.00,Default,,0,0,0,,应该不会那样的吧
Dialogue: 0,1:29:42.16,1:29:44.46,Default,,0,0,0,,湿了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:29:45.06,1:29:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:29:54.96,1:29:58.16,Default,,0,0,0,,又要那样掐？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:15.32,1:30:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:30:19.18,1:30:23.98,Default,,0,0,0,,是因为你那么粗暴地掐我啦
Dialogue: 0,1:30:41.32,1:30:42.52,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:30:43.98,1:30:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,你平时也总是这样掐姐姐的小穴吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:30:49.96,1:30:52.08,Default,,0,0,0,,真是个变态
Dialogue: 0,1:30:59.50,1:31:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,你可以摸，那我也要摸这里咯
Dialogue: 0,1:31:19.22,1:31:21.48,Default,,0,0,0,,我可以看这里吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:31:43.18,1:31:47.20,Default,,0,0,0,,可以舔这个吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:32:17.22,1:32:21.09,Default,,0,0,0,,等等
Dialogue: 0,1:32:21.09,1:32:24.50,Default,,0,0,0,,涨的这么大，我嘴含不住耶
Dialogue: 0,1:33:17.48,1:33:19.36,Default,,0,0,0,,别射了啊
Dialogue: 0,1:34:00.62,1:34:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,要变得湿答答了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:19.68,1:34:22.72,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:34:32.92,1:34:35.84,Default,,0,0,0,,有点激烈呢
Dialogue: 0,1:34:39.54,1:34:42.54,Default,,0,0,0,,肉缝感觉要裂开了
Dialogue: 0,1:34:57.04,1:35:00.32,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:02.33,1:35:06.54,Default,,0,0,0,,都变得湿哒哒的了
Dialogue: 0,1:35:07.54,1:35:08.96,Default,,0,0,0,,稍微...
Dialogue: 0,1:35:14.64,1:35:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,这该怎么办啊？
Dialogue: 0,1:35:26.80,1:35:30.00,Default,,0,0,0,,为了报复，我要狠狠地舔你
Dialogue: 0,1:36:23.60,1:36:25.24,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:37:57.85,1:37:59.70,Default,,0,0,0,,舒服吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:06.44,1:38:08.40,Default,,0,0,0,,想放进去了？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:21.50,1:38:22.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:38:27.54,1:38:31.16,Default,,0,0,0,,想插进我的肉缝深处了吗？
Dialogue: 0,1:38:33.32,1:38:35.40,Default,,0,0,0,,躺下
Dialogue: 0,1:39:13.28,1:39:16.90,Default,,0,0,0,,你真的很喜欢我的这道肉缝呢
Dialogue: 0,1:39:41.98,1:39:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,很热，脱掉吧
Dialogue: 0,1:40:32.32,1:40:35.20,Default,,0,0,0,,要进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:40:48.72,1:40:50.68,Default,,0,0,0,,看...
Dialogue: 0,1:40:50.68,1:40:53.44,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害，要进去了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:08.51,1:41:09.96,Default,,0,0,0,,全都进去了哦
Dialogue: 0,1:41:15.26,1:41:17.14,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:41:19.20,1:41:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,全部插到我的小穴里了
Dialogue: 0,1:41:29.10,1:41:31.24,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:41:47.24,1:41:48.96,Default,,0,0,0,,整根都进去了呢
Dialogue: 0,1:42:13.04,1:42:16.94,Default,,0,0,0,,好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:43:36.44,1:43:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,我的小穴...好舒服
Dialogue: 0,1:43:47.90,1:43:49.84,Default,,0,0,0,,这个好厉害
Dialogue: 0,1:44:33.69,1:44:34.74,Default,,0,0,0,,好厉害...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:15.14,1:45:19.58,Default,,0,0,0,,从后面...插进小穴里
Dialogue: 0,1:45:34.38,1:45:37.17,Default,,0,0,0,,就是这里...
Dialogue: 0,1:45:48.44,1:45:52.90,Default,,0,0,0,,那里...要融化了...
Dialogue: 0,1:57:41.34,1:57:46.38,Default,,0,0,0,,听译字幕\N@98堂最爱X怡\N匠心之作
Dialogue: 0,1:57:46.42,1:57:49.45,Default,,0,0,0,,更多精彩\N尽在98堂@最爱X怡


